1
00:01:40,660 --> 00:01:42,000
=What If=

2
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:44,980
=What If=

3
00:01:44,980 --> 00:01:47,820
=Episode 4=
(When Reality Becomes A Dream)

4
00:02:11,520 --> 00:02:12,720
Why are you back?

5
00:02:16,880 --> 00:02:18,920
I... I came down to pick up my parcel.

6
00:02:19,150 --> 00:02:20,200
Don't lie.

7
00:02:20,510 --> 00:02:21,550
I know you are lying.

8
00:02:22,720 --> 00:02:23,920
What has happened?

9
00:02:26,630 --> 00:02:27,630
My mom

10
00:02:27,920 --> 00:02:30,070
has already rented out this place.

11
00:02:30,771 --> 00:02:33,510
I wanted to discuss it
with you just now.

12
00:02:33,590 --> 00:02:36,590
But you seemed so tired

13
00:02:36,600 --> 00:02:38,620
running between your workplace
and the hospital.

14
00:02:38,630 --> 00:02:41,150
So I didn't tell you.

15
00:02:42,070 --> 00:02:44,320
Since when have you become

16
00:02:44,360 --> 00:02:45,880
so hesitant with me?

17
00:02:47,880 --> 00:02:48,950
Hop on.

18
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:50,150
Let's go to my place.

19
00:03:35,950 --> 00:03:36,950
Yu Jian.

20
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:41,200
Yu Jian.

21
00:03:41,760 --> 00:03:42,800
Are you back...

22
00:04:26,470 --> 00:04:28,200
Put this on and go to bed early.

23
00:04:35,840 --> 00:04:36,630
What's wrong?

24
00:04:36,880 --> 00:04:38,200
It's not your first time here.

25
00:04:38,285 --> 00:04:40,470
You were brave to jump onto my bed
early in the morning

26
00:04:40,470 --> 00:04:41,800
and wake me up that day.

27
00:04:43,200 --> 00:04:44,470
But I'm going to sleep here.

28
00:04:45,200 --> 00:04:46,080
I haven't done this

29
00:04:46,080 --> 00:04:47,470
since growing up.

30
00:04:47,950 --> 00:04:49,200
Why all the worries?

31
00:04:49,510 --> 00:04:50,680
You were terrified just now

32
00:04:50,690 --> 00:04:52,510
as if I had sneaked into my home
like a thief.

33
00:04:52,510 --> 00:04:53,430
It was scary.

34
00:04:58,760 --> 00:04:59,680
Well,

35
00:05:00,320 --> 00:05:01,240
get rest early.

36
00:05:01,250 --> 00:05:04,360
Tomorrow, I will clean up
Yu Yan's room for you.

37
00:05:05,760 --> 00:05:07,150
Would your parents agree?

38
00:05:07,550 --> 00:05:08,470
Of course.

39
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:10,460
Later, I will collect your things

40
00:05:10,550 --> 00:05:11,880
from your mom's place.

41
00:05:12,260 --> 00:05:14,340
You are so kind to me, Yam Head.

42
00:05:16,110 --> 00:05:18,920
If you ever encounter trouble
in the future, don't bear it yourself.

43
00:05:19,510 --> 00:05:21,430
You must tell me immediately.

44
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:22,950
I'm your Yam Head.

45
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:28,070
Get rest early.

46
00:05:29,070 --> 00:05:30,360
Ride safe.

47
00:05:30,470 --> 00:05:31,510
Text me when you arrive.

48
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:33,400
All right.

49
00:05:33,400 --> 00:05:34,320
Go ahead.

50
00:06:17,840 --> 00:06:18,430
Guo?

51
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:19,720
Mrs. Yu,

52
00:06:20,110 --> 00:06:21,360
why are you back?

53
00:06:22,720 --> 00:06:23,800
I'm so forgetful.

54
00:06:23,810 --> 00:06:26,180
I realized I didn't bring my phone
when I was halfway there.

55
00:06:26,200 --> 00:06:27,590
I forgot it.

56
00:06:28,320 --> 00:06:29,400
Were you here

57
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:31,800
last night?

58
00:06:32,070 --> 00:06:32,720
Yes.

59
00:06:34,030 --> 00:06:36,030
I... I forgot my keys.

60
00:06:36,070 --> 00:06:36,680
Then,

61
00:06:36,760 --> 00:06:38,150
Yu Jian brought me back.

62
00:06:38,828 --> 00:06:40,070
Yu Jian came home last night?

63
00:06:40,320 --> 00:06:40,950
He did.

64
00:06:41,200 --> 00:06:43,171
But he headed back
to the hospital afterward.

65
00:06:43,542 --> 00:06:44,890
I'm going to the bathroom, Mrs. Yu.

66
00:06:44,920 --> 00:06:45,840
Sure.

67
00:06:45,880 --> 00:06:48,430
There is a new toothbrush
under the sink.

68
00:06:48,720 --> 00:06:49,760
All right, thank you.

69
00:06:50,110 --> 00:06:51,260
Maybe you can wait for me.

70
00:06:51,260 --> 00:06:53,280
I'll make it quick and
go to the hospital with you.

71
00:06:53,280 --> 00:06:54,110
Okay.

72
00:06:55,110 --> 00:06:56,030
It won't take long.

73
00:07:20,510 --> 00:07:21,880
Gotcha.

74
00:07:25,030 --> 00:07:26,000
What did you just say?

75
00:07:26,010 --> 00:07:27,790
Wang Yan rented the place
to someone else,

76
00:07:27,800 --> 00:07:28,920
so Guo has to stay in ours?

77
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:30,590
Mom,

78
00:07:31,110 --> 00:07:32,900
Guo has been with us since little.

79
00:07:33,110 --> 00:07:34,280
Why all the fuss?

80
00:07:34,760 --> 00:07:36,510
Besides, Yu Yan's room is left unused.

81
00:07:36,880 --> 00:07:37,550
Right.

82
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:39,280
Guo,

83
00:07:39,470 --> 00:07:41,760
you can stay in Yan's room. Don't worry.

84
00:07:42,430 --> 00:07:43,110
Yu Jian,

85
00:07:43,550 --> 00:07:44,800
you are inconsiderate.

86
00:07:45,030 --> 00:07:46,990
How could you not consider Guo at all?

87
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:48,910
She moves into your place
before getting married,

88
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:50,240
people might gossip.

89
00:07:50,430 --> 00:07:52,360
What gossip?

90
00:07:53,070 --> 00:07:55,110
Both of them will
get married sooner or later.

91
00:07:55,550 --> 00:07:57,200
Don't meddle.

92
00:07:59,430 --> 00:08:01,280
Mrs. Yu, don't worry.

93
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:03,680
Maybe Yu Jian didn't explain it clearly.

94
00:08:04,200 --> 00:08:06,320
Actually, I want to rent Yan's room.

95
00:08:06,550 --> 00:08:07,600
I want to rent the room.

96
00:08:08,150 --> 00:08:09,280
How could you say that?

97
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:12,550
If you pay to stay in Yan's room,

98
00:08:13,200 --> 00:08:15,360
it would make us
look like money grabbers.

99
00:08:15,510 --> 00:08:16,840
Drink your chicken soup.

100
00:08:17,920 --> 00:08:18,920
If you mean a rental,

101
00:08:20,190 --> 00:08:21,230
that's all right.

102
00:08:22,350 --> 00:08:23,560
Mom, are you serious?

103
00:08:23,885 --> 00:08:25,485
Do you really want to charge her?

104
00:08:26,760 --> 00:08:28,600
If Guo moves in as a tenant,

105
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:30,110
gossip could be avoided.

106
00:08:30,640 --> 00:08:31,440
Are you saying

107
00:08:33,030 --> 00:08:34,070
that I pay you the rental

108
00:08:34,150 --> 00:08:35,520
for Guo, right?

109
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:36,370
Why are you giving

110
00:08:36,520 --> 00:08:37,520
your mom the money?

111
00:08:37,530 --> 00:08:38,600
Are you out of your mind?

112
00:08:38,720 --> 00:08:39,880
Yeah, you silly.

113
00:08:40,520 --> 00:08:42,360
We are a family.

114
00:08:42,480 --> 00:08:44,190
We won't take Guo's money.

115
00:08:44,310 --> 00:08:45,110
Just drink the soup.

116
00:08:45,640 --> 00:08:46,680
What I mean is,

117
00:08:46,680 --> 00:08:48,240
ask Wang Yan to pay the rent.

118
00:08:48,520 --> 00:08:50,230
Guo, ask for the money from your mom.

119
00:08:50,480 --> 00:08:52,920
She is the one who rented
your place to someone else.

120
00:08:53,030 --> 00:08:55,060
Mom, if Ms. Wang doesn't pay for Guo,

121
00:08:55,190 --> 00:08:56,480
Guo still has to pay.

122
00:08:56,640 --> 00:08:57,560
Shut up.

123
00:08:58,760 --> 00:08:59,440
Mrs. Yu,

124
00:08:59,880 --> 00:09:01,390
since I'm renting the place,

125
00:09:01,680 --> 00:09:03,030
I should pay the rent.

126
00:09:03,640 --> 00:09:05,100
That's settled.

127
00:09:05,110 --> 00:09:06,350
I have to go back to my office.

128
00:09:06,440 --> 00:09:08,440
Mr. Yu, remember to finish
the chicken soup.

129
00:09:08,520 --> 00:09:09,150
I should go.

130
00:09:09,350 --> 00:09:11,020
I know you understand me.

131
00:09:11,310 --> 00:09:12,230
Don't worry, Mrs. Yu.

132
00:09:12,240 --> 00:09:12,950
I'll see you off.

133
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:14,430
It's fine.
I will contact you later.

134
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:15,190
Bye, Mr. Yu.

135
00:09:15,190 --> 00:09:15,920
Bye, Mrs. Yu.

136
00:09:16,030 --> 00:09:16,760
Be careful.

137
00:09:19,030 --> 00:09:19,760
Mom,

138
00:09:19,920 --> 00:09:21,350
are you aware of what you just said?

139
00:09:21,657 --> 00:09:22,460
Ms. Wang could even

140
00:09:22,460 --> 00:09:24,120
charge her own daughter for the rent.

141
00:09:24,150 --> 00:09:25,720
How would she possibly pay for Guo?

142
00:09:25,760 --> 00:09:26,390
That's right.

143
00:09:26,520 --> 00:09:28,600
Didn't I make it clear enough?

144
00:09:28,680 --> 00:09:30,350
I'm not asking Guo for the money.

145
00:09:30,520 --> 00:09:31,720
It's Wang Yan.

146
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:33,740
If she doesn't pay,
she is taking advantage of us.

147
00:09:33,740 --> 00:09:34,760
Understood?

148
00:09:35,840 --> 00:09:37,310
Keep it down.

149
00:09:37,880 --> 00:09:39,390
I get what she is saying.

150
00:09:39,920 --> 00:09:44,190
Your mom wants to

151
00:09:44,270 --> 00:09:45,350
get Guo's money back

152
00:09:45,560 --> 00:09:46,840
from Wang Yan.

153
00:09:46,950 --> 00:09:48,110
Did I get it right?

154
00:09:48,310 --> 00:09:49,742
You are smart for the first time.

155
00:09:50,520 --> 00:09:51,760
Are you dull?

156
00:09:58,640 --> 00:10:00,600
Guo, regarding the rent,

157
00:10:00,885 --> 00:10:02,230
please don't take it to heart.

158
00:10:02,342 --> 00:10:03,390
My mom was just saying.

159
00:10:03,720 --> 00:10:04,920
She won't charge you for that.

160
00:10:06,070 --> 00:10:08,310
I brought up paying rent myself,

161
00:10:08,310 --> 00:10:09,760
so I will pay.

162
00:10:12,190 --> 00:10:12,950
How about this?

163
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:14,314
I give you the money,

164
00:10:14,390 --> 00:10:15,400
and you give it to her.

165
00:10:15,410 --> 00:10:17,114
Well, I give them
an allowance every month.

166
00:10:17,115 --> 00:10:18,440
It's the same.

167
00:10:18,857 --> 00:10:20,640
Listen, if you want to say
or do anything,

168
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:21,857
discuss it with me first.

169
00:10:21,885 --> 00:10:22,870
Don't decide on your own.

170
00:10:22,880 --> 00:10:23,560
Do you hear me?

171
00:10:24,114 --> 00:10:25,371
Please don't get the wrong idea.

172
00:10:25,560 --> 00:10:26,310
I really think

173
00:10:26,390 --> 00:10:27,800
I found a good place to stay.

174
00:10:28,230 --> 00:10:30,150
But you make things complicated.

175
00:10:30,680 --> 00:10:31,520
You have done so much

176
00:10:31,600 --> 00:10:32,800
for my family.

177
00:10:33,190 --> 00:10:35,800
If I were to charge you for the rent,
I wouldn't call myself human.

178
00:10:39,840 --> 00:10:41,350
Since I chose to stay in Leshan,

179
00:10:41,520 --> 00:10:43,560
I chose a life with you.

180
00:10:44,310 --> 00:10:46,150
We will go through
ups and downs together.

181
00:10:46,230 --> 00:10:48,314
All the more reason
that I won't take your money.

182
00:10:53,070 --> 00:10:55,110
Guo, don't worry.

183
00:10:55,440 --> 00:10:57,520
I will provide you with a better life.

184
00:10:57,950 --> 00:10:59,680
You will be much happier

185
00:10:59,840 --> 00:11:01,628
than those who go
to Beijing or Shanghai.

186
00:11:02,440 --> 00:11:03,150
Sure.

187
00:11:03,440 --> 00:11:04,680
You can do it now.

188
00:11:04,840 --> 00:11:05,560
How?

189
00:11:06,110 --> 00:11:07,390
Buy me another Ciba cake,

190
00:11:07,520 --> 00:11:08,760
and I will be happier.

191
00:11:09,270 --> 00:11:10,110
Sure. You can eat it

192
00:11:10,560 --> 00:11:11,520
right now.

193
00:11:18,580 --> 00:11:19,390
Ms. Liu.

194
00:11:19,520 --> 00:11:21,600
Mr. Yu, we are here.

195
00:11:21,880 --> 00:11:23,230
- Dad.
- Guo is here. Jian.

196
00:11:23,714 --> 00:11:24,720
We brought you flowers.

197
00:11:24,880 --> 00:11:26,600
- So beautiful.
- Do you like them?

198
00:11:33,350 --> 00:11:35,990
(Even an ordinary life
can brim with lights.)

199
00:11:36,480 --> 00:11:40,110
(People here live
comfortably and happily.)

200
00:11:59,428 --> 00:12:01,150
- Mr. Yu, drink some water.
- All right.

201
00:12:01,150 --> 00:12:02,720
Dad, Mom.

202
00:12:02,880 --> 00:12:03,640
Jian is here.

203
00:12:03,650 --> 00:12:04,590
- How is it?
- Coming.

204
00:12:04,600 --> 00:12:05,560
Are you tired?

205
00:12:06,200 --> 00:12:07,270
I'm not. Are you?

206
00:12:07,720 --> 00:12:08,440
I'm not.

207
00:12:08,450 --> 00:12:09,250
Have you eaten yet?

208
00:12:09,520 --> 00:12:10,230
Not yet.

209
00:12:10,600 --> 00:12:11,480
Grab a bite.

210
00:12:12,110 --> 00:12:12,800
All right.

211
00:12:12,800 --> 00:12:13,720
You should go back now.

212
00:12:13,730 --> 00:12:15,030
It has been a tiring day for you.

213
00:12:15,070 --> 00:12:16,270
- It's fine.
- Guo.

214
00:12:19,680 --> 00:12:21,190
Here. Bring the fruit with you.

215
00:12:21,520 --> 00:12:22,350
No, Mrs. Yu.

216
00:12:22,350 --> 00:12:23,100
No thanks.

217
00:12:23,100 --> 00:12:25,100
- Keep them.
- Remember to eat while you work.

218
00:12:25,110 --> 00:12:26,630
- Thank you, Mrs. Yu.
- Travel safe.

219
00:12:26,640 --> 00:12:28,270
All right. Come on and eat.

220
00:12:28,980 --> 00:12:29,680
Eat up.

221
00:12:29,680 --> 00:12:30,560
Here.

222
00:12:31,350 --> 00:12:32,150
Be careful.

223
00:12:33,950 --> 00:12:34,600
Yu.

224
00:12:34,880 --> 00:12:36,990
(Isn't this the life)

225
00:12:36,990 --> 00:12:38,640
(many people dream of?)

226
00:12:38,650 --> 00:12:39,390
(Inpatient Department)

227
00:12:39,390 --> 00:12:40,390
(I'm happy)

228
00:12:40,920 --> 00:12:41,950
(living in a small town.)

229
00:12:42,640 --> 00:12:43,840
(How about you in Shanghai?)

230
00:12:44,150 --> 00:12:46,480
(Have you seen the life you dream of?)

231
00:12:50,140 --> 00:12:52,220
(Haowei Annual Celebration)

232
00:13:36,314 --> 00:13:38,485
Is this a custom
of Haowei's annual celebration?

233
00:13:38,720 --> 00:13:39,390
Of course.

234
00:13:39,640 --> 00:13:42,190
We have a different theme each year.

235
00:13:42,350 --> 00:13:44,480
This year, we go for
organic vegetables and fruits.

236
00:13:44,640 --> 00:13:47,020
So, the theme of tonight's banquet

237
00:13:47,020 --> 00:13:48,440
fits very well.

238
00:13:48,800 --> 00:13:49,760
It's interesting.

239
00:13:50,350 --> 00:13:51,480
Ladies and gentlemen,

240
00:13:51,680 --> 00:13:54,760
welcome to Haowei's annual celebration.

241
00:13:54,950 --> 00:13:55,820
First of all,

242
00:13:55,840 --> 00:13:57,680
let's give a big hand to welcome

243
00:13:57,680 --> 00:13:59,920
the general manager of Haowei Group,

244
00:13:59,980 --> 00:14:02,580
Mr. Xue Yuming, to give his speech.

245
00:14:02,680 --> 00:14:03,560
Please.

246
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:07,900
Bravo!

247
00:14:17,720 --> 00:14:19,640
In the past year,

248
00:14:20,640 --> 00:14:21,880
Haowei Group

249
00:14:22,150 --> 00:14:23,990
has been developing steadily.

250
00:14:24,760 --> 00:14:27,190
We seized the opportunities
in various areas

251
00:14:27,720 --> 00:14:30,310
and have achieved remarkable results.

252
00:14:30,760 --> 00:14:32,640
On behalf of the company,

253
00:14:32,650 --> 00:14:34,857
I would like to express my gratitude
to all the staff.

254
00:14:34,920 --> 00:14:35,800
Thank you so much.

255
00:14:38,942 --> 00:14:40,800
I won't say much.
There are surprises later.

256
00:14:40,990 --> 00:14:42,560
I wish you a Happy New Year.

257
00:14:45,542 --> 00:14:47,485
Thank you for your wonderful speech,
Mr. Xue.

258
00:14:47,520 --> 00:14:48,400
Please have a seat.

259
00:14:48,840 --> 00:14:50,440
Next, we will present

260
00:14:50,600 --> 00:14:52,600
the Best Employee of the Year award.

261
00:14:53,030 --> 00:14:55,030
Let's congratulate Zhang Chao.

262
00:14:55,230 --> 00:14:56,990
Well done!

263
00:14:57,230 --> 00:14:58,030
Lv Xiaomeng.

264
00:14:59,310 --> 00:15:00,440
Ping Youyi.

265
00:15:00,920 --> 00:15:01,920
Li Shuang.

266
00:15:02,800 --> 00:15:04,150
Hou Xinjie.

267
00:15:04,520 --> 00:15:05,480
Xia Guo.

268
00:15:20,230 --> 00:15:22,440
Let's invite the award presenter,

269
00:15:22,640 --> 00:15:24,880
the chairman of Haowei Group,

270
00:15:25,190 --> 00:15:26,350
Mr. Lu Wan.

271
00:15:26,480 --> 00:15:27,350
Welcome, Mr. Lu.

272
00:15:30,230 --> 00:15:31,110
Thank you.

273
00:15:38,920 --> 00:15:39,640
Thank you, Mr. Lu.

274
00:15:39,640 --> 00:15:41,114
You have the loudest applause.

275
00:15:43,070 --> 00:15:43,880
Congratulations.

276
00:15:44,980 --> 00:15:47,420
(Best Employee Award,
Certification of Honor)

277
00:15:54,800 --> 00:15:55,680
In the past year,

278
00:15:56,190 --> 00:15:58,680
thank you
to these six excellent employees

279
00:15:58,990 --> 00:16:01,950
and colleagues down there
for your hard work.

280
00:16:02,270 --> 00:16:03,270
I really appreciate it.

281
00:16:06,480 --> 00:16:07,390
It's New Year.

282
00:16:07,520 --> 00:16:09,390
I wish you all a Happy New Year.

283
00:16:09,640 --> 00:16:10,880
- Happy New Year.
