00:27:53,640 --> 00:27:54,960
for my girlfriend too.

562
00:27:55,270 --> 00:27:56,110
What is this?

563
00:27:56,150 --> 00:27:57,030
A moment.

564
00:27:57,760 --> 00:27:59,070
So mysterious.

565
00:28:04,030 --> 00:28:04,920
Let me see.

566
00:28:05,520 --> 00:28:07,840
My gift isn't as expensive as yours.

567
00:28:08,640 --> 00:28:09,430
Promise me

568
00:28:09,880 --> 00:28:10,720
you won't despise it.

569
00:28:11,190 --> 00:28:12,030
I won't.

570
00:28:14,720 --> 00:28:16,720
I plan to change to a bigger one

571
00:28:17,520 --> 00:28:18,720
when I come to Shanghai.

572
00:28:32,230 --> 00:28:35,390
So, please wait here for me.

573
00:28:39,760 --> 00:28:41,310
Is this a comforting gift?

574
00:28:43,600 --> 00:28:45,470
You can take it

575
00:28:45,720 --> 00:28:47,840
as my promise to you.

576
00:28:51,110 --> 00:28:52,430
If so, I will receive it.

577
00:28:54,030 --> 00:28:55,070
I will wait for you.

578
00:28:56,840 --> 00:28:57,680
Later,

579
00:28:58,150 --> 00:28:59,960
we will be together forever

580
00:29:00,110 --> 00:29:01,230
and never leave each other.

581
00:29:01,314 --> 00:29:02,742
We will never leave each other.

582
00:29:04,260 --> 00:29:05,160
So nice.

583
00:29:05,560 --> 00:29:06,150
Do you like it?

584
00:29:06,270 --> 00:29:07,880
I like your gift.

585
00:29:08,142 --> 00:29:09,470
I took a long time to pick it.

586
00:29:32,760 --> 00:29:33,920
Dear Mr. Yu,

587
00:29:34,390 --> 00:29:36,880
you are now
in the vegetables and fruits area.

588
00:29:36,880 --> 00:29:37,960
Pick anything you want.

589
00:29:38,800 --> 00:29:40,000
Thank you, Mrs. Yu.

590
00:29:40,020 --> 00:29:42,700
(Envy apple, 50 yuan each)

591
00:29:45,110 --> 00:29:47,110
An apple costs 50 yuan?

592
00:29:48,110 --> 00:29:49,030
I better put it back

593
00:29:49,030 --> 00:29:50,000
and not damage it.

594
00:29:50,480 --> 00:29:51,310
Look at this.

595
00:29:51,310 --> 00:29:53,390
A giant crab over there.

596
00:29:53,390 --> 00:29:54,840
It's called the red king crab.

597
00:29:56,230 --> 00:29:58,470
How come things are
so expensive in Shanghai?

598
00:29:59,400 --> 00:30:01,030
You said it yourself, this is Shanghai.

599
00:30:01,030 --> 00:30:02,520
That's the price here.

600
00:30:02,680 --> 00:30:03,880
You will get used to it.

601
00:30:04,480 --> 00:30:05,760
Look at the pink fish there.

602
00:30:05,920 --> 00:30:06,920
So interesting.

603
00:30:07,057 --> 00:30:08,920
Think about those three dogs
at the riverside.

604
00:30:10,230 --> 00:30:11,760
I found it Shanghai is bizarre.

605
00:30:11,800 --> 00:30:13,230
Even dogs have their own carts.

606
00:30:13,230 --> 00:30:14,640
They don't have to walk.

607
00:30:15,314 --> 00:30:17,714
People here have nothing better
to spend their money.

608
00:30:17,920 --> 00:30:19,140
Not really.

609
00:30:19,310 --> 00:30:21,680
Ordinary white collars here are like me.

610
00:30:21,690 --> 00:30:23,470
We'll take the cramped subway
at peak hours

611
00:30:23,480 --> 00:30:24,980
and can't sleep more than six hours.

612
00:30:24,990 --> 00:30:26,390
Still, we manage.

613
00:30:27,760 --> 00:30:29,600
But you won't have much happiness.

614
00:30:30,520 --> 00:30:32,390
There are times
when I feel extremely happy.

615
00:30:33,270 --> 00:30:34,110
When?

616
00:30:34,920 --> 00:30:36,270
The payday every month.

617
00:30:36,440 --> 00:30:37,720
I get even happier

618
00:30:37,880 --> 00:30:40,470
when I get both salary and bonus.

619
00:30:41,760 --> 00:30:43,310
In the end, it's all about money,

620
00:30:43,840 --> 00:30:45,000
you money-obsessed.

621
00:30:45,390 --> 00:30:46,350
Are you curious about

622
00:30:46,520 --> 00:30:47,800
how to make your boyfriend

623
00:30:47,800 --> 00:30:48,800
feel extremely happy?

624
00:30:49,310 --> 00:30:50,190
Tell me.

625
00:30:50,920 --> 00:30:53,030
When my girlfriend prepares
delicious food

626
00:30:53,030 --> 00:30:54,520
and feeds it to me,

627
00:30:54,680 --> 00:30:55,800
I'll be over the moon.

628
00:30:56,880 --> 00:30:58,720
In your dream.

629
00:31:00,640 --> 00:31:01,800
Guo, don't run.

630
00:31:53,070 --> 00:31:54,150
Okay, just pull over here.

631
00:31:54,390 --> 00:31:55,390
A bit forward.

632
00:31:55,720 --> 00:31:56,720
Forward.

633
00:32:00,030 --> 00:32:01,270
Mr. Liu, Mr. Li.

634
00:32:01,971 --> 00:32:03,960
I brought you the New Year's goods
for Ms. Nan.

635
00:32:04,000 --> 00:32:06,350
You've worked hard in the past year.
Happy Chinese New Year.

636
00:32:06,350 --> 00:32:07,840
Happy New Year.
Thank you so much.

637
00:32:07,950 --> 00:32:08,960
Over here.

638
00:32:09,310 --> 00:32:10,260
Call everyone over.

639
00:32:10,350 --> 00:32:11,030
Okay.

640
00:32:11,030 --> 00:32:12,270
Guys, come and unload the goods.

641
00:32:12,270 --> 00:32:14,030
- Over here.
- Hurry and unload.

642
00:32:14,030 --> 00:32:15,760
These are Haowei's gift boxes.

643
00:32:15,760 --> 00:32:18,150
They are all delicious food.
Hope this brings you good luck.

644
00:32:18,150 --> 00:32:18,720
Thanks.

645
00:32:18,720 --> 00:32:19,600
Everyone has one set.

646
00:32:19,720 --> 00:32:21,720
- Thank you so much.
- Here you go.

647
00:32:22,070 --> 00:32:22,960
Thank you, Ms. Nan.

648
00:32:22,970 --> 00:32:24,190
Thank you, Marketing Department.

649
00:32:24,190 --> 00:32:25,000
You are welcome.

650
00:32:25,030 --> 00:32:25,640
I have to say

651
00:32:25,840 --> 00:32:26,800
the superiors of Haowei

652
00:32:26,880 --> 00:32:27,760
are so kind.

653
00:32:27,880 --> 00:32:30,190
Look, Mr. Xue
gave us red packets earlier,

654
00:32:30,480 --> 00:32:32,380
and now Ms. Nan has given us
the gift boxes.

655
00:32:32,480 --> 00:32:33,350
- See you, Mr. Xue.
- See you, Mr. Xue.

656
00:32:33,390 --> 00:32:34,030
Happy New Year.

657
00:32:34,030 --> 00:32:35,520
We must work harder.

658
00:32:35,560 --> 00:32:36,390
That's right.

659
00:32:37,070 --> 00:32:38,714
- Hello, Mr. Xue.
- Hello, Mr. Xue.

660
00:32:39,314 --> 00:32:40,142
Thank you, Mr. Xue.

661
00:32:40,150 --> 00:32:41,150
Mr. Xue?

662
00:32:43,628 --> 00:32:45,885
You came here to distribute
the red packets yourself?

663
00:32:45,890 --> 00:32:47,180
What about you? Why are you here?

664
00:32:47,180 --> 00:32:47,800
I...

665
00:32:47,840 --> 00:32:48,960
I represent Ms. Chen

666
00:32:48,960 --> 00:32:50,828
in delivering the New Year's good
to everyone.

667
00:32:51,310 --> 00:32:53,800
It seems Ms. Chen and I thought alike.

668
00:32:54,640 --> 00:32:55,920
But I'm not as lucky as her

669
00:32:56,057 --> 00:32:57,771
to have a capable assistant like you.

670
00:32:57,800 --> 00:32:59,457
That's why I have to come myself.

671
00:32:59,880 --> 00:33:01,150
You must be joking.

672
00:33:06,880 --> 00:33:07,720
Here's your share.

673
00:33:08,880 --> 00:33:09,920
No thanks, Mr. Xue.

674
00:33:10,310 --> 00:33:11,390
Happy New Year.

675
00:33:14,880 --> 00:33:15,920
Thank you, Mr. Xue.

676
00:33:18,342 --> 00:33:19,390
I have only seen you smile

677
00:33:19,390 --> 00:33:20,470
under two circumstances.

678
00:33:21,720 --> 00:33:23,230
One is when you get money.

679
00:33:23,950 --> 00:33:24,880
Seems like it.

680
00:33:29,070 --> 00:33:30,000
I'm sorry.

681
00:33:31,180 --> 00:33:32,780
(Tensai, Hengshan Road branch)

682
00:33:34,760 --> 00:33:36,350
And another one is like now.

683
00:33:37,270 --> 00:33:38,030
Your boyfriend?

684
00:33:39,771 --> 00:33:41,310
I remember that you won a smartphone

685
00:33:41,310 --> 00:33:42,390
during the annual dinner.

686
00:33:42,390 --> 00:33:43,350
Why aren't you using it?

687
00:33:46,030 --> 00:33:47,230
The old one still works.

688
00:33:51,880 --> 00:33:52,840
Go on.

689
00:33:53,800 --> 00:33:54,640
Okay. Right away.

690
00:33:57,600 --> 00:33:58,885
Do you have plans later?

691
00:33:59,057 --> 00:34:01,114
Come with me to distribute red packets.

692
00:34:01,485 --> 00:34:04,920
But Ms. Nan asked me to deliver
the New Year's goods to other stores.

693
00:34:04,990 --> 00:34:05,920
It's fine.

694
00:34:06,228 --> 00:34:07,714
Do you drive? I can give you a lift.

695
00:34:08,070 --> 00:34:09,230
I came here in this truck.

696
00:34:09,880 --> 00:34:10,600
If so, you may go.

697
00:34:12,070 --> 00:34:12,760
See you, Mr. Xue.

698
00:34:13,190 --> 00:34:14,110
Drive safe.

699
00:34:14,200 --> 00:34:15,150
All right. Thank you.

700
00:34:15,190 --> 00:34:15,800
Come.

701
00:34:15,800 --> 00:34:16,840
I can do it myself.

702
00:34:16,840 --> 00:34:17,800
Thank you, Mr. Xue.

703
00:34:19,840 --> 00:34:20,560
Careful.

704
00:34:20,560 --> 00:34:21,230
I'm good.

705
00:34:22,310 --> 00:34:23,150
Let's go, sir.

706
00:34:24,480 --> 00:34:25,030
Bye-bye.

707
00:34:25,230 --> 00:34:26,270
Bye-bye.

708
00:34:40,500 --> 00:34:42,030
(BFC)

709
00:34:42,030 --> 00:34:43,560
- Hi, sir. How many of you?
- Hello.

710
00:34:43,600 --> 00:34:44,150
Two, please.

711
00:34:44,230 --> 00:34:45,840
All right. Here is your queue number.

712
00:34:45,840 --> 00:34:46,840
All right, thank you.

713
00:34:46,840 --> 00:34:47,680
You are welcome.

714
00:34:47,680 --> 00:34:49,840
(Tensai)

715
00:34:49,840 --> 00:34:50,640
Hello, Guo.

716
00:34:51,190 --> 00:34:52,700
Where are you?

717
00:34:52,740 --> 00:34:53,480
I have arrived.

718
00:34:53,500 --> 00:34:54,542
(Tensai)
At the entrance.

719
00:34:54,720 --> 00:34:55,560
Entrance?

720
00:34:56,190 --> 00:34:57,070
I can't see you.

721
00:34:57,070 --> 00:34:58,680
Where are you? Wave your hands.

722
00:34:59,480 --> 00:35:00,190
No. 50.

723
00:35:00,990 --> 00:35:01,880
Do you see me now?

724
00:35:02,030 --> 00:35:02,960
No.

725
00:35:03,560 --> 00:35:05,760
Hengshan Road's Tensai
is inside the mall,

726
00:35:05,760 --> 00:35:06,470
right?

727
00:35:07,030 --> 00:35:07,960
Where?

728
00:35:08,990 --> 00:35:11,070
I... I'm at BFC.

729
00:35:11,720 --> 00:35:13,840
But the one you sent me
is on Hengshan Road.

730
00:35:13,840 --> 00:35:15,500
Why did you go to BFC?

731
00:35:15,500 --> 00:35:16,470
Well, I will come to you.

732
00:35:16,520 --> 00:35:17,270
Wait.

733
00:35:17,440 --> 00:35:18,428
Forget it. Stay there.

734
00:35:18,560 --> 00:35:19,430
I will come to you.

735
00:35:20,520 --> 00:35:21,470
Bye-bye.

736
00:35:36,640 --> 00:35:37,760
So what if you are a member?

737
00:35:37,800 --> 00:35:39,880
It means I don't have to queue,

738
00:35:40,190 --> 00:35:41,150
do you understand?

739
00:35:41,160 --> 00:35:42,480
You have to wait in line even so.

740
00:35:42,480 --> 00:35:43,740
It's all the same in every city.

741
00:35:43,880 --> 00:35:45,470
What's wrong? Let's go inside.

742
00:35:45,800 --> 00:35:47,350
This fellow is making a fuss.

743
00:35:47,350 --> 00:35:48,240
Said I cut the line

744
00:35:48,350 --> 00:35:49,560
and wouldn't let me in.

745
00:35:49,990 --> 00:35:51,470
We don't have to queue.

746
00:35:52,440 --> 00:35:53,430
Everyone is queuing,

747
00:35:53,430 --> 00:35:54,760
why don't you need to queue?

748
00:35:54,760 --> 00:35:55,790
You can ask the staff.

749
00:35:55,800 --> 00:35:57,470
Just ignore him. Let's go.

750
00:35:57,470 --> 00:35:58,270
Stand right there.

751
00:35:58,990 --> 00:35:59,680
Why?

752
00:36:00,190 --> 00:36:01,110
Are you done yet?

753
00:36:01,680 --> 00:36:02,840
I just want things to be fair.

754
00:36:03,070 --> 00:36:04,230
Everyone is queuing.

755
00:36:04,230 --> 00:36:05,430
Why don't you have to?

756
00:36:05,430 --> 00:36:06,800
How could you cut the line?

757
00:36:17,150 --> 00:36:17,880
Mr. Xue?

758
00:36:17,880 --> 00:36:18,600
Xia Guo.

759
00:36:19,257 --> 00:36:20,000
What has happened?

760
00:36:20,190 --> 00:36:20,920
He...

761
00:36:21,640 --> 00:36:23,310
This is Mr. Xue of my company.

762
00:36:24,480 --> 00:36:26,560
This is Yu Jian, my boyfriend.

763
00:36:29,760 --> 00:36:30,800
Your boyfriend?

764
00:36:31,720 --> 00:36:32,600
I'm so sorry.

765
00:36:33,680 --> 00:36:34,230
Mr. Xue.

766
00:36:34,510 --> 00:36:35,914
Mister, there is a misunderstanding.

767
00:36:35,920 --> 00:36:38,030
In our restaurant, the east section is
for customers,

768
00:36:38,030 --> 00:36:40,030
while the west section
is only for members.

769
00:36:40,270 --> 00:36:41,600
Mr. Xue is one of our members.

770
00:36:41,680 --> 00:36:43,390
He just needs to
make a call before coming.

771
00:36:43,514 --> 00:36:44,742
No need to wait for a table.

772
00:36:45,440 --> 00:36:46,110
If so,

773
00:36:46,390 --> 00:36:47,840
how can I get your membership?

774
00:36:47,950 --> 00:36:49,110
Well, I'm sorry.

775
00:36:49,520 --> 00:36:51,680
You have to spend a certain amount here,

776
00:36:51,742 --> 00:36:54,228
and also a recommendation
from an existing member to join.

777
00:36:54,440 --> 00:36:55,680
So troublesome.

778
00:36:55,680 --> 00:36:56,470
I'm sorry, Mr. Xue.

779
00:36:56,470 --> 00:36:57,150
It's fine.

780
00:36:57,390 --> 00:36:58,390
You may go.

781
00:36:58,390 --> 00:36:59,180
We know each other.

782
00:36:59,230 --> 00:37:00,040
We'll chat for a bit.

783
00:37:00,070 --> 00:37:00,640
Sure.

784
00:37:01,800 --> 00:37:02,800
It's all right.

785
00:37:04,390 --> 00:37:05,470
So, this is your boyfriend.

786
00:37:06,270 --> 00:37:07,960
Yes, he just came to Shanghai,

787
00:37:07,960 --> 00:37:09,260
and he is not familiar with here.

788
00:37:09,270 --> 00:37:10,000
I'm sorry.

789
00:37:10,000 --> 00:37:10,960
It's all right.

790
00:37:11,150 --> 00:37:11,880
Your colleague?

791
00:37:11,880 --> 00:37:12,520
Right.

792
00:37:13,171 --> 00:37:14,590
No wonder I find her face familiar.

793
00:37:14,600 --> 00:37:16,350
We met at the company before.

794
00:37:16,350 --> 00:37:17,420
I'm Xia Guo.

795
00:37:17,840 --> 00:37:19,190
Hello. Just call me Emma.

796
00:37:19,310 --> 00:37:19,960
Hello.

797
00:37:20,030 --> 00:37:21,228
Since it's a misunderstanding,

798
00:37:21,950 --> 00:37:22,760
it's understandable

799
00:37:23,428 --> 00:37:25,285
that it's his first time here.
Don't mind it.

800
00:37:25,600 --> 00:37:26,680
We will go inside first.

801
00:37:27,950 --> 00:37:28,960
Sure.

802
00:37:29,440 --> 00:37:30,470
Let's go.

803
00:37:41,230 --> 00:37:42,070
Yam Head,

804
00:37:42,080 --> 00:37:43,800
it suddenly hits me
that another restaurant

805
00:37:43,800 --> 00:37:45,150
is even better than this one.

806
00:37:45,150 --> 00:37:46,430
Let's go there, all right?

807
00:37:47,270 --> 00:37:48,640
Let's go. It's nippy out here.

808
00:37:48,640 --> 00:37:50,560
Come on. Let's go there.

809
00:37:50,560 --> 00:37:53,060
(Tensai)

810
00:38:00,942 --> 00:38:02,140
Excuse me, here's your chilies.

811
00:38:02,150 --> 00:38:02,800
Thank you.

812
00:38:02,800 --> 00:38:04,030
The beef will be served later.

813
00:38:04,070 --> 00:38:04,640
Please enjoy.

814
00:38:04,640 --> 00:38:05,430
Sure.

815
00:38:07,150 --> 00:38:07,880
Eat up.

816
00:38:08,520 --> 00:38:09,310
I have no appetite.

817
00:38:13,771 --> 00:38:15,110
We are in another restaurant now.

818
00:38:15,110 --> 00:38:16,270
Are you still mad?

819
00:38:16,840 --> 00:38:17,760
Guo.

820
00:38:19,800 --> 00:38:22,430
Did I embarrass you earlier?

821
00:38:22,760 --> 00:38:23,840
No.

822
00:38:23,840 --> 00:38:25,060
Don't overthink.

823
00:38:25,190 --> 00:38:27,514
You were waiting in the cold air.
You must be hungry now.

824
00:38:27,680 --> 00:38:28,600
Hurry and eat.

825
00:38:28,610 --> 00:38:29,800
The food here is delicious.

826
00:38:29,800 --> 00:38:30,600
Try it.

827
00:38:31,310 --> 00:38:32,520
Your general manager

828
00:38:33,390 --> 00:38:34,640
is so arrogant.

829
00:38:36,270 --> 00:38:37,430
That woman

830
00:38:38,190 --> 00:38:39,230
must be the same as him.

831
00:38:39,350 --> 00:38:41,470
You didn't see their attitude

832
00:38:41,470 --> 00:38:42,880
before you arrived.

833
00:38:43,640 --> 00:38:45,390
It was a misunderstanding.

834
00:38:46,030 --> 00:38:47,800
They didn't argue much with you, right?

835
00:38:48,230 --> 00:38:50,030
Mr. Xue may seem a bit stoic,

836
00:38:50,270 --> 00:38:52,190
but he treats the staff quite well.

837
00:38:52,520 --> 00:38:55,430
Why are you taking his side?

838
00:38:56,520 --> 00:38:58,190
I didn't take his side.

839
00:38:58,310 --> 00:38:59,860
I'm just telling the truth.

840
00:38:59,950 --> 00:39:02,820
You can't judge them
over a trivial matter.

841
00:39:03,110 --> 00:39:03,800
You know,

842
00:39:04,440 --> 00:39:06,030
Dr. Jiang from Hospital Ruihua

843
00:39:06,110 --> 00:39:07,350
is a friend of Mr. Xue's.

844
00:39:07,680 --> 00:39:09,000
He introduced the doctor to me

845
00:39:09,030 --> 00:39:10,270
because he knew we needed help.

846
00:39:11,920 --> 00:39:14,800
So, let's be more generous,

847
00:39:15,270 --> 00:39:16,230
all right?

848
00:39:17,840 --> 00:39:19,230
Well, let's eat up.

849
00:39:19,520 --> 00:39:20,430
Try this.

850
00:39:23,142 --> 00:39:23,870
How does it taste?

851
00:39:23,880 --> 00:39:24,840
Nice?

852
00:39:26,150 --> 00:39:29,800
Yes, but we waited
for another 40 minutes.

853
00:39:30,390 --> 00:39:32,840
Everyone has to queue
for good restaurants in Shanghai.

854
00:39:32,942 --> 00:39:34,840
Besides, the Chinese New Year
is approaching,

855
00:39:34,840 --> 00:39:36,190
many people choose to dine out.

856
00:39:36,480 --> 00:39:38,920
It's lucky for us to
only wait for half an hour.

857
00:39:39,480 --> 00:39:42,760
They are lots of restaurants like this
in Zhanggong Bridge.

858
00:39:42,800 --> 00:39:45,470
There are all along the entire street,
and no need to queue.

859
00:39:45,680 --> 00:39:47,020
Can it be the same?

860
00:39:47,390 --> 00:39:49,480
The labor and rent here

861
00:39:49,560 --> 00:39:51,070
are much higher than in our hometown.

862
00:39:51,350 --> 00:39:53,880
Besides, the service industry
here is exceptional.

863
00:39:54,230 --> 00:39:55,760
It's not just about eating a meal,

864
00:39:55,950 --> 00:39:57,800
they provide you
with good emotional value.

865
00:39:59,950 --> 00:40:01,150
Guo, you have changed.

866
00:40:02,230 --> 00:40:03,430
How?

867
00:40:04,520 --> 00:40:07,550
Before, you would always drool
when I talked about good food in Leshan.

868
00:40:07,560 --> 00:40:09,680
But now, you think great
of everything in Shanghai.

869
00:40:09,950 --> 00:40:11,430
Waiting in line for a meal,

870
00:40:12,190 --> 00:40:13,760
easy to get lost, and you need to

871
00:40:13,770 --> 00:40:15,270
take a cab
for only five kilometers.

872
00:40:15,310 --> 00:40:16,190
All this hassle

873
00:40:16,390 --> 00:40:17,880
makes you sleep two hours less.

874
00:40:19,680 --> 00:40:21,150
Do you really like all these?

875
00:40:21,150 --> 00:40:22,190
Well, I...

876
00:40:26,840 --> 00:40:27,800
All right,

877
00:40:28,070 --> 00:40:29,800
I know you are angry.

878
00:40:31,030 --> 00:40:31,960
Let me tell you.

879
00:40:32,310 --> 00:40:33,960
When I first came to Shanghai,

880
00:40:34,310 --> 00:40:35,840
I was frustrated.

881
00:40:36,230 --> 00:40:37,310
When I took a cab,

882
00:40:37,350 --> 00:40:39,110
the driver spoke in Shanghainese

883
00:40:39,150 --> 00:40:40,510
and I couldn't understand a word.

884
00:40:40,520 --> 00:40:41,110
In the end,

885
00:40:41,110 --> 00:40:42,560
he took me to a place I didn't know.

886
00:40:42,685 --> 00:40:44,230
Besides, the clients embarrassed me,

887
00:40:44,342 --> 00:40:45,942
and my colleagues walked over me.

888
00:40:46,150 --> 00:40:48,350
I'm a foreigner here,
and not familiar with this place.

889
00:40:48,350 --> 00:40:49,680
There used to be lots of trouble.

890
00:40:50,230 --> 00:40:51,390
But what could I do?

891
00:40:51,760 --> 00:40:52,800
Everyone is the same.

892
00:40:53,070 --> 00:40:55,000
We strive to survive every day

893
00:40:55,310 --> 00:40:57,110
and we manage to get through.

894
00:40:59,950 --> 00:41:00,840
Guo,

895
00:41:01,480 --> 00:41:02,640
is this really good for you?

896
00:41:03,110 --> 00:41:04,600
Big cities are complicated.

897
00:41:05,085 --> 00:41:06,520
Aren't you tired of living like this?

898
00:41:07,230 --> 00:41:08,600
I'm living the life myself,

899
00:41:08,600 --> 00:41:10,470
so I have my own judgments and feelings.

900
00:41:11,190 --> 00:41:13,470
Besides, I just received
the Best Employee award.

901
00:41:13,920 --> 00:41:15,190
Don't underestimate me, okay?

902
00:41:15,840 --> 00:41:17,150
I know you are ambitious

903
00:41:17,520 --> 00:41:18,840
and can endure hardships.

904
00:41:19,800 --> 00:41:21,470
But we only live once.

905
00:41:22,070 --> 00:41:23,960
Why stress yourself out?

906
00:41:24,270 --> 00:41:25,230
Do you think

907
00:41:25,230 --> 00:41:26,350
I didn't notice

908
00:41:26,720 --> 00:41:27,960
