922
00:41:56,840 --> 00:41:58,190
You are handsome when you smile.

923
00:42:00,990 --> 00:42:01,800
Well.

924
00:42:02,190 --> 00:42:04,110
Shanghai isn't as scary as you imagine.

925
00:42:04,350 --> 00:42:05,230
Besides,

926
00:42:05,390 --> 00:42:07,390
