more capable than me.

927
00:42:07,560 --> 00:42:09,190
You can manage even if anything happens.

928
00:42:09,560 --> 00:42:10,310
Right?

929
00:42:11,440 --> 00:42:12,390
Most importantly,

930
00:42:12,640 --> 00:42:13,600
I'm here.

931
00:42:14,440 --> 00:42:15,760
I will always stay with you.

932
00:42:16,310 --> 00:42:17,310
Still mad?

933
00:42:17,400 --> 00:42:18,885
Still pulling the long face?

934
00:42:19,350 --> 00:42:20,350
Let's eat.

935
00:42:20,571 --> 00:42:22,350
Hurry and serve me some duck blood tofu.

936
00:42:22,350 --> 00:42:23,230
Here you go.

937
00:42:45,230 --> 00:42:47,680
Mom, are you at the hospital?

938
00:42:49,110 --> 00:42:50,470
Yu Yan is with you?

939
00:42:51,230 --> 00:42:53,560
Good, I'm relieved then.

940
00:42:54,190 --> 00:42:55,350
Guo is doing quite well.

941
00:42:55,350 --> 00:42:56,560
I'll go back a few days later.

